Title: Grundfos Magna 3 D 32-120 F 220 circulating pump 1 x 230V PN6/10
Description: Ideal for creating high performance heating and cooling systems, the Grundfos MAGNA3 32 - 120 F single phase circulator pump is suitable for new installations and refits, offering excellent efficiency and built-in communication capabilities.
